PyStoch: Stochastic Python
--------------------------

Installation
------------

Run the following command, replacing "your/path/pystoch" with the
desired location for the repository:

> git clone https://github.com/jhamrick/pystoch.git your/path/pystoch

And add the following lines to your ~/.bashrc:

export PATH="your/path/pystoch/bin:$PATH"
export PYTHONPATH="your/path/pystoch/src:$PYTHONPATH"

Running
-------

To run a PyStoch program:

> pystoch yourprogram.py

or

> pystoch yourprogram.pystoch

To compile a PyStoch program "yourprogram.py" to "yourprogram.pystoch":

> pystoch_compile yourprogram.py


